BuildRequires:    R-utils 
Requires:         R-CRAN-Rcpp >= 0.11.2
Requires:         R-CRAN-lpSolve 
Requires:         R-stats 
Requires:         R-utils 

%description
A toolbox for systemic risk based on liabilities matrices. Contains a
Gibbs sampler for liabilities matrices where only row and column sums of
the liabilities matrix as well as some other fixed entries are observed.
Includes models for power law distribution on the degree distribution.

